<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Complete Your Stripe Setup</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f9f9f9; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); overflow: hidden;">
            
            <!-- Header -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #0682ca; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #fff;">
                <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 22px;">Action Required: Complete Your Stripe Setup</h2>
              </td>
            </tr>
            
            <!-- Body -->
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 30px; color: #333; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6;">
                <p>Hi <strong><%= userDetail?.first_name %> <%= userDetail?.last_name %></strong>,</p>
                <p>We noticed that your <strong>Stripe account setup</strong> is still incomplete. To start receiving payments without interruption, please provide the missing required details.</p>
                
                <h3 style="color: #ff4d4d; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;">Missing Information:</h3>
                <ul style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 10px 0;">
                  <%- formattedFields %>
                </ul>
                
                <p>Please update your details as soon as possible to ensure your account is fully activated.</p>
                
                <!-- CTA Button -->
                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                  <a href="<%= onboardingLink %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; color: #ffffff; background-color: #0682ca; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">
                    Complete Your Setup
                  </a>
                </p>
                
                <p>If you need help, feel free to contact our support team anytime.</p>
                <p>Best regards, <br><strong>Idispatch Mobility</strong></p>
              </td>
            </tr>
            
            <!-- Footer -->
            <tr>
              <td style="background-color: #f1f1f1; text-align: center; padding: 15px; font-size: 13px; color: #555;">
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Idispatch Mobility. All rights reserved.
              </td>
            </tr>
            
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
